Indian Oil Issues First Tender to Buy Crude Oil for September

-- B y   S h e r r y   S u
-- 
2011-07-01T08:53:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-01/indian-oil-issues-first-tender-to-buy-crude-oil-for-september.html
Indian Oil Corp., the country’s
biggest refiner, issued its first tender for crude oil for
loading in September, official documents obtained by Bloomberg
News showed.  The company bought a total of 8 million barrels of West
African crude for loading in August through two spot tenders.  Details of the company’s requirements are as follows:  To contact the reporter on this story:
